{"id": "1349016583682654248", "channel_id": "1349016583682654248", "type": 0, "author_id": "1326878892664815632", "author_name": "tianfang5580", "author_bot": false, "content": "视频发布在B站，可直接点击下方链接观看【忘却前夜相位对弈(PVP)刷牌队攻略-哔哩哔哩】 https://b23.tv/eY5VqOs\n这套阵容强度很高，我在上赛季用这套阵容打到了3600分，对于想冲分的玩家来说是很好的选择。同时这套卡组因为玩法，用来刷18号的活动也会非常方便，每局出的牌会很多。\n核心内容都在图里，下面是一些感想\n18号那个活动可以说很抽象了，连我一个天天打pvp的玩家都觉得肝起来会很费劲的。只能说大家加油吧\n\n下面是往期的攻略链接，都是这个版本还能用的阵容\n【忘却前夜相位对弈(PVP)塔薇星天鼠队攻略-哔哩哔哩】 https://b23.tv/jkyJYex\n【忘却前夜相位对弈(PVP)幻影队攻略-哔哩哔哩】 https://b23.tv/ymj6wUr\n【忘却前夜相位对弈(PVP)罗坦打击队攻略-哔哩哔哩】 https://b23.tv/UW4DZK5", "timestamp": "2025-03-11T13:50:17.066000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}], "attachments": [{"id": "1349016584072728616", "filename": "1741647865092569129895277656035.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 456796, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349016583682654248/1349016584072728616/1741647865092569129895277656035.jpg?ex=69cbd119&is=69ca7f99&hm=ba5ae5d1fb0d69e61029157ee3d537e5525ee12170627c6be99a4e09cbde7eac&"}, {"id": "1349016584781303818", "filename": "17416980755174856894393845424906.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 631526, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349016583682654248/1349016584781303818/17416980755174856894393845424906.jpg?ex=69cbd119&is=69ca7f99&hm=20afdcac72607e840402dcdff79ae317c8a90193409061d4e709be0948a9dd73&"}, {"id": "1349016585272168489", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-02-25-20-35-16-770_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 235486, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349016583682654248/1349016585272168489/Screenshot_2025-02-25-20-35-16-770_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbd119&is=69ca7f99&hm=ca61a1ec0752fa86cded9e34ab47692ab5a8a5c20f299a4d2bde5894b62e6e82&"}, {"id": "1349016585754644603", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-03-10-20-59-53-542_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg",